<title>USA: Avix Ventures says to buy 51.7 pct of OneWave.</title>
<headline>Avix Ventures says to buy 51.7 pct of OneWave.</headline>
<dateline>WATERTOWN, Mass. 1997-05-02</dateline>
<text>
<p>Avix Ventures LP and OneWave Inc said Friday Avix has agreed to buy about 7.75 million shares of OneWave common stock for a minimum of $8 million, plus future contingent consideration.</p>
<p>The companies said the shares represent 51.7 percent of OneWave's outstanding stock.</p>
<p>The companies said the deal is scheduled to close on or about May 15.</p>
<p>The companies said the sellers include Sundar Subramaniam, a director of the OneWave, and three other OneWave stockholders.</p>
<p>Avix is a privately-held company.</p>
